<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
	<title>Donate Page</title>
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo.png" />
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/donate.css" />
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<img src="/images/logo.png" style="
						height: 50px;
						width: 50px;
						border-radius: 50px;
						margin-right: 10px;
					" />
			<a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Shelter Mission</a>
			<button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
				data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false"
				aria-label="Toggle navigation">
				<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
			</button>
			<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
				<ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="/donate">Donate</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="/info">Information</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="/map">Map</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item dropdown">
						<a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" id="navbarDropdownBlog" href="#" data-toggle="dropdown"
							aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
							<%= emailAddress %>
						</a>
						<div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdownBlog">
							<a class="dropdown-item" href="/logout">Logout</a>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<section class="py-5">
		<div class="container">
			<h1 class="mb-4 display-4 text-center">Homeless Shelters You can Donate To</h1>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
					<div class="card h-100 text-center">
						<img class="card-img-top" src="/images/hope.jpg" alt="..." />
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title">Window of Hope</h4>
							<h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
								KwaZulu-Natal
							</h6>
							<p class="card-text">
								The Window of Hope Program focuses on two
								types of groups: orphans and less privileged
								children; and the destitute and homeless The
								aim is to assist through giving out food
								hampers, clothes and blankets which the
								above mentioned groups lack and are in
								desperate need of. The program targets to
								reach at least an average of 100 different
								people every month (25 people per week) for
								the next 24 months (2 years) in Durban which
								will amount to a total of 2400 heads that
								the program would have helped.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="card-footer text-center">
							<a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://newlifeshelter.net/">Donate Here</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
					<div class="card h-100 text-center">
						<img class="card-img-top" src="/images/haveno.jpg" alt="..." />
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title">
								The Haven Night shelter
							</h4>
							<h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
								Western Cape
							</h6>
							<p class="card-text">
								The Haven Night Shelter was established in
								1978 in Cape Town, South Africa. We were
								registered as a Section 21 (a) (Not for
								Gain) Public Company in 1983, a Non Profit
								Organisation in 2000, and as a Public
								Benefit Organisation in 2004.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="card-footer text-center">
							<a class="btn btn-primary"
								href="https://www.payfast.co.za/donate/go/thehavennightshelterwelfareorganisation">Donate
								Here</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
					<div class="card h-100 text-center">
						<img class="card-img-top" src="/images/fridahart.jpg" alt="..." />
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title">
								Frida Hartley Organisation
							</h4>
							<h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
								Gauteng
							</h6>
							<p class="card-text">
								The Frida Hartley Shelter (FHS) for
								destitute women and children in Yeoville,
								Johannesburg, takes in homeless women and
								their children who have endured neglect,
								abuse, trauma and homelessness. We shelter
								individuals who have lost their jobs and are
								struggling to make ends meet; young homeless
								mothers looking to kick-start their lives;
								and individuals going through financial
								difficulties (affected by retrenchment or
								unemployment).
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="card-footer text-center">
							<a class="btn btn-primary"
								href="https://www.payfast.co.za/donate/go/fridahartleyshelterforwomen">Donate Here</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
					<div class="card h-100 text-center">
						<img class="card-img-top" src="/images/homelesssolution.jpg" alt="..." />
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title">Homeless Solutions</h4>
							<h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
								Gauteng
							</h6>
							<p class="card-text">
								Dear friend, we would like to welcome you to
								Homeless Solutions as a Steward for ACTION.
								Provided you welcome the invitation, what
								this entails is that you will be providing
								our organization with your time and
								expertise in terms of Knowledge,
								spirituality and resources support for the
								well-being of our beneficiaries as whole.
								Help us build a culture of love, stability
								and discipline. Only with your involvement
								and support, can we be able to do it all,
								and believe that all is possible.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="card-footer text-center">
							<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://gogetfunding.com/homeless-solutions/">Donate
								Here</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
					<div class="card h-100 text-center">
						<img class="card-img-top" src="/images/helpingthose.jpg" alt="..." />
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title">
								Helping Those In Need
							</h4>
							<h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
								Eastern Cape
							</h6>
							<p class="card-text">
								This NPO was started by a couple in January
								2017 and is called “Helping Those In Need".
								They feed numerous families and the homeless
								alongside fostering abused & abandoned
								children.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="card-footer text-center">
							<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.helpingthoseineed.co.za">Donate Here</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
					<div class="card h-100 text-center">
						<img class="card-img-top" src="/images/salvationarmy.jpg" alt="..." />
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title">Salvation Army</h4>
							<h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
								Mpumalanga
							</h6>
							<p class="card-text">
								The Salvation Army has an active and vibrant
								outreach, whether through its faith
								communities or its community work. Thousands
								of people – ranging in age from new-born to
								the elderly – depend on the outreach of The
								Salvation Army, through soup kitchens, homes
								for children, rehabilitation centres, or
								home-based care for the sick and elderly, to
								mention some of the ways in which we care
								for people. Without the support of The
								Salvation Army, life would be that much more
								difficult and sometimes unbearable for many
								of them.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="card-footer text-center">
							<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.givengain.com/d/c/2443#amount">Donate Here</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<hr class="my-0" />

	<hr class="my-0" />
	<footer class="py-5">
		<div class="container">
			<p class="m-0 text-center text-white">
				Copyright &copy; Shelter Mission 2021
			</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>

</html>